{
  "stem": "18572.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 389.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were also some of the-- because my stepfather was involved in the Betar, sometimes some of these people would come to our house.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was smuggling of arms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember hiding-- that there were guns or other things were being hidden in our bathroom, under a tub or something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was very, you know-- very macho, very much marching around and looking forward to going and fighting and being a soldier.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my sister was born in Eschwege, so I think she was, like, more involved with taking care of my sister and, you know-- and the baby and all.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my stepfather was very much involved.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was very much involved in the-- in the running of the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and-- and in the Betar, as I said, there were-- on several occasions, some of these people from the Irgun would come to our house, you know?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember I had a bicycle, and that we used to-- the kids used to go out to, like-- I guess it was like an abandoned air-- you know, a airfield or whatever, ride our bikes.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember having just a lot of freedom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The camp was surrounded, you know, with barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's sort of ironic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're liberated and you're back-- in back of-- in back of the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there was no sense of not being able to go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my sense is of the kids just having a free hand-- you know, just running around.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in school or playing as a group-- very much as a group.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were very much, you know, into our own groups of running around and doing things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you ever have any contact with the German civilian population during--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
